snippet.title: Cube Escape: Harvey's Box Trailer [Rusty Lake]
snippet.description:
Promo for Cube Escape: Harvey's Box

It's 1969 and Harvey is trapped inside a box moving to Rusty Lake...Find out what's going on and help Harvey escape by solving numerous of puzzles.

Download now for iOS (Iphone and Ipad):
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/cube-escape-harveys-box/id999924447
Download on Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.CubeEscapeHarveysBox
Or play on web:
http://www.rustylake.com/room-escape-games/cube-escape-harveys-box.html
